软件包 android.text.style 的分层结构

软件包分层结构：
所有软件包

类分层结构

  • java.lang.Object
    • android.text.style.AlignmentSpan.Standard (implements android.text.style.AlignmentSpan, android.text.ParcelableSpan)
    • android.text.style.BulletSpan (implements android.text.style.LeadingMarginSpan, android.text.ParcelableSpan)
    • android.text.style.CharacterStyle
      • android.text.style.BackgroundColorSpan (implements android.text.ParcelableSpan, android.text.style.UpdateAppearance)
      • android.text.style.ClickableSpan (implements android.text.style.UpdateAppearance)
        • android.text.style.URLSpan (implements android.text.ParcelableSpan)
      • android.text.style.ForegroundColorSpan (implements android.text.ParcelableSpan, android.text.style.UpdateAppearance)
      • android.text.style.MaskFilterSpan (implements android.text.style.UpdateAppearance)
      • android.text.style.MetricAffectingSpan (implements android.text.style.UpdateLayout)
        • android.text.style.AbsoluteSizeSpan (implements android.text.ParcelableSpan)
        • android.text.style.RelativeSizeSpan (implements android.text.ParcelableSpan)
        • android.text.style.ReplacementSpan
          • android.text.style.DynamicDrawableSpan
            • android.text.style.ImageSpan
        • android.text.style.ScaleXSpan (implements android.text.ParcelableSpan)
        • android.text.style.StyleSpan (implements android.text.ParcelableSpan)
        • android.text.style.SubscriptSpan (implements android.text.ParcelableSpan)
        • android.text.style.SuperscriptSpan (implements android.text.ParcelableSpan)
        • android.text.style.TextAppearanceSpan (implements android.text.ParcelableSpan)
        • android.text.style.TypefaceSpan (implements android.text.ParcelableSpan)
      • android.text.style.RasterizerSpan (implements android.text.style.UpdateAppearance)
      • android.text.style.StrikethroughSpan (implements android.text.ParcelableSpan, android.text.style.UpdateAppearance)
      • android.text.style.UnderlineSpan (implements android.text.ParcelableSpan, android.text.style.UpdateAppearance)
    • android.text.style.DrawableMarginSpan (implements android.text.style.LeadingMarginSpan, android.text.style.LineHeightSpan)
    • android.text.style.IconMarginSpan (implements android.text.style.LeadingMarginSpan, android.text.style.LineHeightSpan)
    • android.text.style.LeadingMarginSpan.Standard (implements android.text.style.LeadingMarginSpan, android.text.ParcelableSpan)
    • android.text.style.QuoteSpan (implements android.text.style.LeadingMarginSpan, android.text.ParcelableSpan)
    • android.text.style.TabStopSpan.Standard (implements android.text.style.TabStopSpan)

接口分层结构

  • android.text.style.ParagraphStyle
    • android.text.style.AlignmentSpan

    • android.text.style.UpdateLayout
